OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start in Cornwall,
OL,6,Fotherwise rather grey with the odd
OL,7,Fspot of light rain. Skies will
OL,8,Fgradually turn brighter this afternoon
OL,9,Fwith some sunshine developing later
OL,10,Ffrom the east. Feeling cooler than
OL,11,Fyesterday with a brisk easterly breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA bright evening for most
OL,14,Fwith some late sunshine. Overnight
OL,15,Fremaining dry with plenty of clear
OL,16,Fskies, although a few showers may move
OL,17,Fwest along the south coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
