OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA dry and sunny day for
OL,6,Fmuch of the region, however parts of
OL,7,FCornwall and west Devon may see some
OL,8,Fshowers at times. A windy day with
OL,9,Fcoastal gales possible.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry,
OL,12,Fwarm and sunny again for many on
OL,13,FThursday but a threat of further
OL,14,Fshowers towards Cornwall. Showers
OL,15,Fpotentially become more widespread on
OL,16,FFriday and Saturday, but winds also
OL,17,Feasing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
